{
  "stem": "15938.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was gray and navy stripes, just an ordinary-- a straight dress, which we didn't wear after a time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'll tell you about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, on the pocket, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we tried to kind of everybody finding somebody they knew or recognized and keep together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very bad because I had nobody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where sisters kept together and some odd mother here and there with a child, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyhow, I found some friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we bunked into the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the morning, we were woken up by the kapos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- I don't know, 3 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We all had to line up, which was called the Zahlappell, you know, for counting, in rows of four and lines of four, standing there for hours still, till somebody came to count us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was very, very, very, very cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we were allocated a job, which I stayed till I was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a place called Kanada.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now Kanada, it was nicknamed Kanada, because it was a richer type of place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because it was near the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we took the belongings of the people who went into the crematorium to sort.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was on the sorting commando, which meant any clothes or anything which came into the camp went to this particular place where I worked.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were sorting, the dishes, some shoes, you know, sorting out all the-- but it was near the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And sometimes we had to go to the crematorium to pick up the belongings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after a few months, we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We even slept there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't have to walk to the other camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was our job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was hard work, because it was long hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
